n class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>the<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>District<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>. <a id=\"paragraph-355\" class=\"section-permalink\" href=\"\/\/localhost\/admin\/parser.php#7\">\u00b6<\/a><\/p><\/section>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"c\"><p>c. <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>No<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>more<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>than<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>one<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> (<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>1<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>) <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>employee<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>may<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>participate<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>in<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>a<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>Fulbright<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>Teacher<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>Exchange<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>Program<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>in<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>any<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>school<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span> <span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>year<span class=\"dictionary\"><\/span>. <a id=\"paragraph-356\" class=\"section-permalink\" href=\"\/\/localhost\/admin\/parser.php#c\">\u00b6<\/a><\/p><\/section>","plain_text":"                                     CONTRACT\n\nFULBRIGHT TEACHER EXCHANGE LEAVE (\u00a7 14.09)\n\na. An employee with at least (5) years of continuous employment with the\nSpringboro Community City School District dating from the employee\u2019s most\nrecent date of hire may, with permission of the BOARD be entitled to take a\nleave of absence from teaching duties with full salary and benefits for up to\none (1) year to participate in Fulbright Teacher Exchange Program.\n\nb. Participation in the Fulbright Exchange Program shall be subject to the\nfollowing conditions:\n\n1. The year the employee participates in the Fulbright Exchange Program shall\ncount as a year of service in the Springboro Community City Schools.\n\n2. Application for permission to participate much be submitted prior to\nSeptember 1 in the year preceding the year in which the leave is to be taken.\n\n3. The Fulbright Teacher Exchange Program must approve the employee\u2019s\nparticipation in the program and must provide an exchange replacement employee\nto the School District to teach in the position of Springboro employee granted\nthe leave from assigned teaching duties at no cost to the BOARD for any wages,\nbenefits or other expense of the provided employee.\n\n4. The employee, who must agree to work for the Springboro Community City School\nDistrict for one (1) year following completion of the program, shall be returned\nto his\/her same position upon return.\n\n5. Participation in the Exchange Program shall result in no additional cost to\nthe District.\n\n6. The exchange employee shall not be deemed an employee of the School District\nbut shall be subject to all rules, regulations and policies of the BOARD, the\nsame as an employee who would bound by such rules, regulations and policies.\n\n7. If the exchange employee, for whatever reason, cannot fulfill his\/her\nresponsibilities for the term of the exchange, the Springboro employees shall\nreturn to the District at such time as the exchange employee leaves the\nDistrict.\n\nc. No more than one (1) employee may participate in a Fulbright Teacher Exchange\nProgram in any school year.\n","next_section":{"id":"76","structure_id":"15","section_number":"14.10","catch_line":"Job Sharing","url":"http:\/\/localhost\/14.10\/","api_url":"http:\/\/localhost\/api\/law\/14.10\/"},"previous_section":{"id":"74","structure_id":"15","section_number":"14.08","catch_line":"Professional Leave","url":"http:\/\/localhost\/14.08\/","api_url":"http:\/\/localhost\/api\/law\/14.08\/"},"text":{"0":{"id":"347","text":"An employee with at least (5) years of continuous employment with the Springboro Community City School District dating from the employee\u2019s most recent date of hire may, with permission of the BOARD be entitled to take a leave of absence from teaching duties with full salary and benefits for up to one (1) year to participate in Fulbright Teacher Exchange Program.","type":"section","prefixes":["a"],"prefix":"a","entire_prefix":"a","prefix_anchor":"a","level":1,"next_prefix":"b"},"1":{"id":"348","text":"Participation in the Fulbright Exchange Program shall be subject to the following conditions:","type":"section","prefixes":["b"],"prefix":"b","entire_prefix":"b","prefix_anchor":"b","level":1,"prior_prefix":"a","next_prefix":"1"},"2":{"id":"349","text":"The year the employee participates in the Fulbright Exchange Program shall count as a year of service in the Springboro Community City Schools.","type":"section","prefixes":["1"],"prefix":"1","entire_prefix":"1","prefix_anchor":"1","level":1,"prior_prefix":"b","next_prefix":"2"},"3":{"id":"350","text":"Application for permission to participate much be submitted prior to September 1 in the year preceding the year in which the leave is to be taken.","type":"section","prefixes":["2"],"prefix":"2","entire_prefix":"2","prefix_anchor":"2","level":1,"prior_prefix":"1","next_prefix":"3"},"4":{"id":"351","text":"The Fulbright Teacher Exchange Program must approve the employee\u2019s participation in the program and must provide an exchange replacement employee to the School District to teach in the position of Springboro employee granted the leave from assigned teaching duties at no cost to the BOARD for any wages, benefits or other expense of the provided employee.","type":"section","prefixes":["3"],"prefix":"3","entire_prefix":"3","prefix_anchor":"3","level":1,"prior_prefix":"2","next_prefix":"4"},"5":{"id":"352","text":"The employee, who must agree to work for the Springboro Community City School District for one (1) year following completion of the program, shall be returned to his\/her same position upon return.","type":"section","prefixes":["4"],"prefix":"4","entire_prefix":"4","prefix_anchor":"4","level":1,"prior_prefix":"3","next_prefix":"5"},"6":{"id":"353","text":"Participation in the Exchange Program shall result in no additional cost to the District.","type":"section","prefixes":["5"],"prefix":"5","entire_prefix":"5","prefix_anchor":"5","level":1,"prior_prefix":"4","next_prefix":"6"},"7":{"id":"354","text":"The exchange employee shall not be deemed an employee of the School District but shall be subject to all rules, regulations and policies of the BOARD, the same as an employee who would bound by such rules, regulations and policies.","type":"section","prefixes":["6"],"prefix":"6","entire_prefix":"6","prefix_anchor":"6","level":1,"prior_prefix":"5","next_prefix":"7"},"8":{"id":"355","text":"If the exchange employee, for whatever reason, cannot fulfill his\/her responsibilities for the term of the exchange, the Springboro employees shall return to the District at such time as the exchange employee leaves the District.","type":"section","prefixes":["7"],"prefix":"7","entire_prefix":"7","prefix_anchor":"7","level":1,"prior_prefix":"6","next_prefix":"c"},"9":{"id":"356","text":"No more than one (1) employee may participate in a Fulbright Teacher Exchange Program in any school year.","type":"section","prefixes":["c"],"prefix":"c","entire_prefix":"c","prefix_anchor":"c","level":1,"prior_prefix":"7"}}}